repo_metadata.description: This repository contains only PHP files to support Composer installation. This repository is a mirror of [protobuf](https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf). Any support requests, bug reports, or development contributions should be directed to that project. To install protobuf for PHP, please see https://github.com/protocolbuffers/protobuf/tree/master/php

owner_record.name: Protocol Buffers
owner_record.description: A language-neutral, platform-neutral extensible mechanism for serializing structured data.

advisories.title: protobuf susceptible to buffer overflow
advisories.description: protobuf allows remote authenticated attackers to cause a heap-based buffer overflow.

advisories.title: NULL Pointer Dereference in Protocol Buffers
advisories.description: Nullptr dereference when a null char is present in a proto symbol. The symbol is parsed incorrectly, leading to an unchecked call into the proto file's name during generation of the resulting error message. Since the symbol is incorrectly parsed, the file is nullptr. We recommend upgrading to version 3.15.0 or greater.
